Basic GRanges containing promoters

Source: R/data.R
ex_prom.Rd

Promoters from an example region

ex_prom

Format

Simple GRanges object to demonstrate using features in various steps implemented in this package

All annotations are from GRCh37

Examples

data(ex_prom)
ex_prom
